Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices NW Real Estate

data.description: Country charmer close to town, on almost half an acre, with low taxes! Tons of updates, beautifully remodeled kitchen with appliances. Three-car garage and plenty of parking for RV and room for toys. New well motor and pressure pump, ductless heat pump, electrical panel, hot water heater within the last few years. Ductless heat/cooling units in living room and primary bedroom. Third bedroom with closet is also ideal for a den, crafts/sewing or home office space. Both full bathrooms have nice updates and tub/showers.  Family room pre-plumbed for wood/pellet stove.  Pretty yard for entertaining, lawn games and celebrations. Ideal primary residence or vacation property with Woahink and Siltcoos Lakes and Florence's coveted sand dunes just a stone's throw away.  Ideal home for fishing/recreational use with room to store a boat or ATV's.  Easy access to Honeyman State Park and just 20 minutes to Winchester Bay.  Plenty of parking.
